{
  "stem": "8569.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They believed that maybe by building the bunkers and all kinds of hiding places, they can survive rather than to fight.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were, of course, a Jewish council who were-- who were doing anything to appease the Germans by bribes and money.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And give them money, and again money, and pay them again and again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Until one day, Czerniakow, who was then the president of the Jewish community, was asked again to give money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was no money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he, in desperation, committed suicide rather then cooperate with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you know, this was the mood in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it's-- we need to-- to think of the dynamic constellation of the ghetto not very different than the dynamic constellation of any other place when you have suddenly this little categories of the older people, rich people, poor people.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody protecting their own vested interests.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had heroes and you had robbers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have smugglers on a big scale that became very rich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had the intelligentsia that could no longer-- use their intellect that became very poor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a-- a confusion of values.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had your share of heroes and robbers, and people that were taking advantage of being taken advantage of.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a market in the ghetto where people were selling their personal possessions in exchange for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With the decrees that the [NON-ENGLISH] decreed against the Jews, and one of the things was that the Jews couldn't have pianos.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember my father selling the pianos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a Pole came into our house, and he gave him some money and took-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and took-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
